title: Haralson's playoff hopes dashed with home loss
text: Haralson's playoff hopes dashed with home loss File Photo by Lisa Hughes Nov 3, 2023 Nov 3, 2023 Updated 8 hrs ago Facebook WhatsApp SMS Print Copy article link Save Haldyn Williams rushed for two touchdowns as Haralson County fell to Fannin County, 41-14. File Photo by Lisa Hughes As featured on Haralson's playoff hopes dashed with home loss Haralson County lost the battle of Rebels at home on senior night Friday, falling to Fannin County 41-14. The loss prevents Haralson from making the 2A playoffs for the second season in a row.
